OL,3,CRoyal Mail takeover by Czech
OL,4,Cbillionaire given Government approval
OL,6,FThe takeover by Daniel Kretinsky's EP
OL,7,FGroup from current owner International
OL,8,FDistribution Services was confirmed by
OL,9,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,10,Fon Monday morning.
OL,12,FHe said the takeover was secured along
OL,13,Fwith legally binding commitments with
OL,14,FMr Kretinsky's EPH Group over the
OL,15,Fpostal service, including protecting
OL,16,Fthe one-price-goes-anywhere delivery
OL,17,Fcommitment and a pledge to keep Royal
OL,18,FMail headquartered in the UK.
