OL,6,FMr Reynolds said: "For too many years
OL,7,Fprogress on securing a stable future
OL,8,Fat Royal Mail has stalled, but from
OL,9,Fday one we have been committed to
OL,10,Fproviding a secure future for
OL,11,Fthousands of workers and customers."
OL,13,FHe added the agreements reached with
OL,14,FEPH Group showed "we are working
OL,15,Ftowards ensuring a financially stable
OL,16,FRoyal Mail with protected links
OL,17,Fbetween communities other providers
OL,18,Fcan't reach".
