OL,6,FThe deal between Kretinsky and Royal
OL,7,FMail's parent company is #3.6 billion
OL,8,F` or #5.3 billion including debt.
OL,10,FEPH has also reached an agreement to
OL,11,Frecognise and negotiate with the
OL,12,Funions representing Royal Mail's
OL,13,Ffrontline staff and managers ` the
OL,14,FCommunication Workers Union (CWE) and
OL,15,FUnite respectively ` for at least the
OL,16,Fnext five years.
OL,18,FUnions are reported to have been
OL,19,Fpushing for further assurances and for
OL,20,Fthe commitment over compulsory
OL,21,Fredundancies to be extended.
