OL,6,FOn Friday, Royal Mail was fined #10.5
OL,7,Fmillion by regulator Ofcom for missing
OL,8,Fits post-delivery targets in the 2023-
OL,9,F2024 financial year.
OL,11,FThe watchdog said just under three-
OL,12,Fquarters of first class post was
OL,13,Fdelivered on time during the period,
OL,14,Fwell short of its 93% target, and
OL,15,F92.7% of second-class post was
OL,16,Fdelivered on time, below its 98.5%
OL,17,Ftarget.
